window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>A ménage à trois romance stretches from the clear, warm ocean to the lush, rolling mountains of Montego Bay, Jamaica.</b></p> <p>Emily once again finds herself in the throes of unforgettable passion and irresistible power as she dives deeper into the love of two men and the dangerous world they inhabit. As for Ballad and Rothschild, they're not yet done with Emily. Not by a long shot.</p> <p><i>Pervade Montego Bay</i> is book two in the new romance duet by <i>USA Today</i> best-selling author Vanessa Fewings.</p> <p>Sip the rum. Taste the desire. <b><i>See you on the island.</i></b></p>"; 
